The paper deals with biomedical image segmentation using deep learning, which is a common topic in computer vision (cs.CV) and machine learning (cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.DL). The focus on gastric cancer and the use of partial annotation may also suggest a connection to medical imaging (cs.IR).
